@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5260
@BaseUrl = {{Api_HostAddress}}/v1/todos

# Variables for testing
@TestTitle = Complete project documentation
@TestDescription = Write comprehensive documentation for the new feature including API docs and user guides

### Create a new Todo
POST {{BaseUrl}}/create-todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{TestTitle}}",
  "description": "{{TestDescription}}"
}

### Create Todo with different data
POST {{BaseUrl}}/create-todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Setup CI/CD pipeline",
  "description": "Configure GitHub Actions for automated testing and deployment"
}

### Create Todo for testing
POST {{BaseUrl}}/create-todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Review code changes",
  "description": "Perform code review for the latest pull requests"
}

### Error Cases

### Create Todo with empty title (should return 400)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/create-todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "This should fail due to empty title"
}

### Create Todo with empty description (should return 400)
POST {{BaseUrl}}/create-todo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Valid title",
  "description": ""
}
